(3, 'UPPSC Assistant Town Planner ATP Recruitment 2023 Apply Online for 24 Post', '21', '40', 'Bachelor Degree OR PG Diploma in Town and Country Planning in Any Recognized University in India OR Associate Membership of at Least One of the Following Institute of Planners / Americal Institute of Town Planner / Members of Institute of Town Planner London OR Institute of Town Planner India OR Equivalent Qualification of London or US.', 'General / OBC / EWS : 125/- SC / ST : 65/- PH Candidates : 25', 'Uttar Pradesh Public Service Commission (UPPSC) has issued an Assistant Town Planner Examination Post Notification 2023. For Recruitment details, pay scale, age limit, selection prcedure, job information and all other information, read the advertisement and then apply.\n\n\n\n', 'https://uppsc.up.nic.in/CandidatePages/Notifications.aspx ', '14-08-2023', '21-09-2023', '15-09-2023', '1'),
(5, 'UPPSC Staff Nurse (Male / Female) Recruitment 2023 Apply Online for 2240 Post', '21', '40', '? Class 10th with Science and 10+2 Intermediate Exam with Diploma in General Nursing and Midwifery OR B.SC Nursing Degree\n? Registration Certificate in UP Nursing Council\n? More Eligibility Read the Notification', 'General / OBC / EWS : 125/- SC / ST : 65/- PH Candidates : 25', 'Uttar Pradesh Public Service Commission (UPPSC) has issued an Staff Nurse (Male / Female) Examination Post Notification 2023.. For Recruitment details, pay scale, age limit, selection prcedure, job information and all other information, read the advertisement and then apply.', 'https://uppsc.up.nic.in/CandidatePages/Notifications.aspx ', '21-08-2023', '29-09-2023', '15-09-2023', '1'),
(6, 'Coal India Limited CIL Management Trainee 2023 Apply Online for 560 Post', 'NA', '30', 'For Mining / Civil Trade : Engineering Degree BE / B.Tech / B.Sc Engineering in Related Branch with 60% Marks.\nSC / ST Candidates : 55% Marks.\nFor Geology : M.Sc. / M.Tech. in Geology or Applied Geology / Geophysics or Applied Geophysics with minimum 60% marks\nGATE 2023 Score Card Required\nMore Details Read the Notification.', ' General / OBC : 1180/- SC / ST : 0/- (Nil) PH : 0/- (Nil)', 'Coal India Limited CIL has released the notification for the recruitment of 560 Management Trainee MT Based on GATE 2023 Score Card. All the candidates who are interested in this CIL MT Latest Management Trainee 2023. See the advertisement for information related to age limit, syllabus, State wise post, selection procedure, pay scale in CIL Recruitment 2023.', 'https://cdn.digialm.com/EForms/configuredHtml/1258/82592/Index.html ', '13-09-2023', '12-10-2023', '15-09-2023', '1'),
(7, 'Reserve Bank of India RBI Assistant Recruitment 2023 Apply Online for 450 Post', '20', '28', 'Bachelor Degree in Any Stream with 50% Marks.\nKnow the Local Language.', 'General / OBC / EWS: 450/- SC / ST : 50', 'Reserve Bank of India (RBI) has released the detailed notification of Assistant Post whose advertisement Year is 2023. Read the official notification for Reserve Bank of India Assistant Recruitment eligibility, age limit, syllabus, selection procedure, exam pattern, state wise recruitment and all other details.\n\n', 'https://ibpsonline.ibps.in/rbiaaaug23/ ', '13-09-2023', '04-10-2023', '15-09-2023', '1'),
(8, ' \nUPSSSC Forest Guard / Wild Life Guard Recruitment 2023 Apply Online for 709 Post', '18', '40', 'UPSSSC PET 2022 Score Card.\n10+2 Intermediate Exam in Any Recognized Board in India.\nPhysical Eligibility :\nHeight :\nMale : 168 CMS, For ST: 160 CMS\nFemale : 150 CMS, For ST : 82 CMS\nRunning :\nMale : 25 Km in 4 Hours with 10KG Weight\nFemale : 14 Km in 4 Hours\nMore Details Read the Notification', 'General / OBC / EWS : 25/- SC / ST : 25/- PH (Dviyang) : 25', 'Uttar Pradesh Subordinate Service Selection Commission (UPSSSC)has released the Forest Guard / Wild Life Guard recruitment advertisement for 709 posts. Read the notification for recruitment eligibility, post information, selection procedure, age limit, pay scale and all other information.\n\n\n', 'https://bit.ly/3pA3Wgj ', '20-09-2023', '10-10-2023', '15-09-2023', '1'),
(9, 'UPSSSC Junior Assistant, Junior Clerk and Assistant Grade III Recruitment 2023 Apply Online for 3831 Post', '18', '40', '? UPSSSC PET 2022 Score Card.\n? 10+2 Intermediate Exam in Any Recognized Board in India.\n? Hindi Typing 25 WPM and English Typing 30 WPM\n? NIELIT CCC Exam Passed\n? More Details Read the Notification.', ' General / OBC / EWS : 25/- SC / ST : 25/- PH (Dviyang) : 25', 'Uttar Pradesh Subordinate Service Selection Commission (UPSSSC)has released the Junior Assistant, Junior Clerk and Assistant Grade III recruitment advertisement for 3831 posts. Read the notification for recruitment eligibility, post information, selection procedure, age limit, pay scale and all other information.', 'https://bit.ly/3pA3Wgj ', '12-09-2023', '03-10-2023', '15-09-2023', '1'),
(10, 'Jharkhand JSSC Lady Supervisor Combined Competitive Exam - JLSCE 2023 Apply Online for 444 Post', '18', '38', 'Only for Female\nBachelor Degree in Sociology / Psychology / Home Science\nMore Eligibility Details Read the Notification', 'General / OBC / EWS : 100/- SC / ST : 50', 'Jharkhand Staff Selection Commission (JSSC)has released the Jharkhand Lady Supervisor Competitive Exam JLSCE 2023 recruitment advertisement for 444 posts. Read the notification for recruitment eligibility, post information, selection procedure, age limit, pay scale and all other information.\n', 'https://jssc.nic.in/application-forms-apply ', '26-09-2023', '25-10-2023', '15-09-2023', '1'),
(11, 'Rajasthan RPSC Statistical Officer Recruitment 2023 Apply Online for 72 Post', '21', '40', '\n? Master Degree in Economics / Statistics / Mathematics with Paper in Statistics / Commerce with Statistics / M.Sc Agriculture Statistics and RS-CIT Course Certificate\n? 1 Year Experience\n? Knowledge of Rajasthani Culture.\n? More Details Read the Notification.', 'General / Other State : 600/- OBC / BC : 400/- SC / ST : 400/- Correction Charge : 500', 'Rajasthan Public Service Commission has released the advertisement of Statistical Officer 72 Post. For other information related to recruitment like syllabus, age limit, qualification, pay scale and all other information read the advertisement and then apply.', 'https://sso.rajasthan.gov.in/signin ', '15-09-2023', '14-10-2023', '15-09-2023', '1');
